<div style="text-align: center;">
<h4 id="toc0"><span>A Business Dinner</span></h4>
<p>Collabcon entry involving MC&amp;D and Oneiroi Collective<br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> <span class="error-inline"><em>AlanDaris</em> does not match any existing user name</span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/arbelict" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4305778); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4305778&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721433" alt="Arbelict" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4305778)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/arbelict" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4305778); return false;">Arbelict</a></span><br />
<strong>The second part of the storyline:</strong> <a href="/scp-4363">SCP-4363</a></p>
<h3 id="toc1"><span><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/alandaris">~~ More Alan Stuff ~~</a></span></h3>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
